In Interview repeated questions are
=======================================

1. For suppose I have 2 slave servers with in these 2 slave servers we need to install web servers write a playbook for this, but the tricky is here
one slave server is have amazon-linux and another salve server is ubuntu server

in amazon-linux we will do install httpd
for in ubuntu-linux we will do install apache2

how to reolve this to write playbook is based on the Operating System we will do use CONDITONS

and also WHEN condition as well

Redhat or amazon-linux is same

when condiction
==================

slave-------> os --------> RedHat----> httpd
slave-------> OS --------> Ubuntu ----> apache2

start writing playbook for this

vim condtions.yml

---
- hosts: ops
  connection: ssh

  tasks:
    - name: install webserver on RedHat
      yum: name=httpd state=present
      when: ansible_os_family=="RedHat"

    - name: install webserver on Ubuntu
      apt: name=apache2 state=present
      when: ansible_os_family=="Ubuntu"

